title: California's Iconic Case Study House #26
description:
Stay at a gem of modern architecture, Case Study House 26!
Of the few remaining Case Study Houses, it is the only one available for vacation rental, a true classic of California Case Study House program.
Built in 1963 and well-maintained and where needed updated for modern living comfort, it will make for a truly unique experience.
Even if you're not a design lover, this place offers a serene places to relax, enjoy nature, food & wine, or visit the many nearby sites (Napa, Pacific Ocean, SF).
extraInfo:
Kids over 14 are OK. The house is not fully childproof. If you're children are younger than 14 and you like to stay, please contact us.
No pets. No smoking. No parties.

From time to time our 'G' calendar sync seems to fail. We try to keep our calendar updated, but please excuse if not all available days are actually available.
